      <title>特朗普第二届政府执政期间，加密货币领域“几乎”所有人都是赢家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/-almost-everyone-in-crypto-s-a-winner-in-a-second-trump-administration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普再次担任总统的背景下，那些在美国上市受阻的比特币矿工和加密货币公司最终可能会成为数字资产领域的最大赢家。面临失去市场份额风险的外国公司最终可能会成为最大的输家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/-almost-everyone-in-crypto-s-a-winner-in-a-second-trump-administration</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加沙发现脊髓灰质炎病毒痕迹，引发疫情担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/war-in-gaza-who-warns-of-polio-potential-after-virus-traces-found</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在饱受战争蹂躏的加沙地带的水源中发现了 2 型变异脊髓灰质炎病毒的痕迹后，人道主义组织正在考虑为加沙地带的巴勒斯坦人开展大规模疫苗接种活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/war-in-gaza-who-warns-of-polio-potential-after-virus-traces-found</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 11:42:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>遭受停电打击的伊拉克开始通过新线路进口土耳其电力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/blackout-hit-iraq-begins-importing-turkish-power-with-new-line</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其和伊拉克之间规划了20年的一条输电线路开始运营，有可能帮助这个产油阿拉伯国家解决严重的停电问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-21/blackout-hit-iraq-begins-importing-turkish-power-with-new-line</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 11:24:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
